Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical Latin literature from 45 BC, making it over 2000 years old. Richard McClintock, a Latin professor at Hampden-Sydney College in Virginia, looked up one of the more obscure Latin words, consectetur, from a Lorem Ipsum passage, and going through the cites of the word in classical literature, discovered the undoubtable source. Lorem Ipsum comes from sections 1.10.32 and 1.10.33 of "de Finibus Bonorum et Malorum" (The Extremes of Good and Evil) by Cicero, written in 45 BC. This book is a treatise on the theory of ethics, very popular during the Renaissance. The first line of Lorem Ipsum, "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet..", comes from a line in section 1.10.32.

Processed meat is often considered as a very strong risk factor of cancer. The question is- is it the meat that cause cancer or it is the ingredients that are used for processing? 
Many chemicals are used during processing for meat and fish. Some of these chemicals may produce some by products that may cause cancer.
This is a great initiative to start such a platform for academics. Thank you Mustak; my friend, my first cibling.

fields.personal_info: Django is a powerful framework for writing Python web applications. Using a full-featured framework like Django allows you to get your applications and sites up and running quicker without having to worry about the common structural code to tie it together. Frameworks let you focus on the unique portions of your application and let the tools do the heavy lifting.
I am an assitant professor in the University of Dhaka. I am empathic and believe in the sharing of resources- both intellectual and  tangible. Welcome to my network
Assistant professor computational intelligence at Vrije Universiteit Amsterdam
Assistant Professor of Biochemistry, Directorate General of Health Service, Mohakhali, Dhaka, Bangladesh. Attached: Magura Medical College, Magura.

Hello. This is Ananya Azad!: Currently working on my M.Sc  thesis in 'Bioresources Technology and Industrial Biotechnology Laboratory' of Department of Biotechnology & Genetic Engineering, Jahangirnagar University. Alongside academic field I have a keen interest in knowledge learning and sharing which inspired me to work as a freelance feature writer in an online media house. Travelling and visiting new places is among one of my topmost favorite activities. I have a very intense affection towards cooking and foods, love to know about and try out different recipes and ingredients. Love to read, shop, plying paddleboats and making my tastebuds go through different street foods. Dream to build career in the field of research and development. I believe myself to be a happy soul, born to fly at it's free will. Welcome to my realm!☺
I want to see a world where no one dies from a misdiagnosis. I'll do what I can to attain that goal.
